codeSystems.name: Advance_Directives_VS
codeSystems.title: Advance Directives
codeSystems.description: This value set lists the interventions that the patient may choose to accept or decline in their advance directives.

codeSystems.name: Alcohol_USe_Frequency_VS
codeSystems.title: Alcohol USe Frequency
codeSystems.description: This value set lists the frequency metrics to express the frequency of alcohol use (e.g. drinks per day, drinks per week).

codeSystems.name: Antepartum_Education_VS
codeSystems.title: Antepartum Education
codeSystems.description: This value set identifies the types of pregnancy-related education that may be delivered to the patient.

codeSystems.name: Antepartum_Family_History_and_Genetic_Screening_VS
codeSystems.title: Antepartum Family History and Genetic Screening
codeSystems.description: This value set includes the type of genetic-related risks identified through screening of the patient’s and biological father’s family history.

codeSystems.name: Antepartum_History_of_Infection_VS
codeSystems.title: Antepartum History of Infection
codeSystems.description: This value set identifies the infections that may result in risk to the pregnancy or otherwise inform the birth plan.

codeSystems.name: Antepartum_History_of_Past_Illness_VS
codeSystems.title: Antepartum History of Past Illness
codeSystems.description: This value set identifies conditions that may impact the pregnancy care and monitoring decisions.

codeSystems.name: Antepartum_Laboratory_VS
codeSystems.title: Antepartum Laboratory
codeSystems.description: This value set identifies the laboratory tests that may be ordered and monitored during pregnancy.

codeSystems.name: Antepartum_Review_of_Systems_Menstrual_History_VS
codeSystems.title: Antepartum Review of Systems Menstrual History
codeSystems.description: Antepartum Review of Systems Menstrual History This value set identifies the menstrual-history related observations that may inform the pregnancy care.

codeSystems.name: Edema_VS
codeSystems.title: Edema observation
codeSystems.description: This value set lists the expected values for the Edema observation.

codeSystems.name: Fetal_Movement_VS
codeSystems.title: Fetal Movement
codeSystems.description: This value set lists the expected values for the Fetal Movement observation.

codeSystems.name: Fetal_Presentation_VS
codeSystems.title: Fetal Presentation
codeSystems.description: This value set lists the expected values for the Fetal Presentation observation.

codeSystems.name: Presence_In_Urine_VS
codeSystems.title: Presence In Urine
codeSystems.description: This value set lists the expected values for the Presence In Urine observation.
codeSystems.StructureDefinition-IHE.GlucosePresencei: Albumin Presence In Urine test by strip

codeSystems.name: Smoking_Status_VS
codeSystems.title: Smoking Status
codeSystems.description: This value set identifies whether the patient is a smoker (everyday smoker or some day smoker) or whether the patient was a previous smoker.

codeSystems.name: Smoking_Tabbacco_Use_Frequency_VS
codeSystems.title: Smoking Tabbacco Use Frequency
codeSystems.description: This value set identifies the frequency of tobacco use in packs/day, packs/week, or packs/year.
